OL,3,CChaos expected as more transport staff
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,FTransport chaos is expected as staff
OL,7,Ffrom Transport for Greater Manchester
OL,8,F(TfGM) begin a fresh round of strike
OL,9,Faction over pay.
OL,11,FThe new strike action, on 12 December,
OL,12,Fcomes as more than 200 Unite members,
OL,13,Fworking for TfGM, began industrial
OL,14,Faction in October, striking alongside
OL,15,Ftheir colleagues in the Unison union.
OL,17,FThe latest dispute has been over pay,
OL,18,Fwith workers rejecting a "below
OL,19,Finflation" 3.2% pay rise.
