OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,FThey are demanding an increase that
OL,7,Freflects the rising cost of living and
OL,8,Fthe increased workloads they say have
OL,9,Fbeen taken on since the creation of
OL,10,Fthe Bee Network.
OL,12,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,13,Fcriticised the employer's actions,
OL,14,Fstating: "TfGM's behaviour towards
OL,15,Fthese workers is atrocious. Our
OL,16,Fmembers have put forward a reasonable
OL,17,Fpay request that TfGM can more than
OL,18,Fafford to meet.
