OL,3,CChaos expected as more transport staff
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,F"Strikes will continue with Unite's
OL,7,Ffull support until TfGM returns to
OL,8,Ftalks and puts forward an acceptable
OL,9,Foffer."
OL,11,FThe new TfGM strikes are scheduled for
OL,12,F12, 13, 19, and 20 December,
OL,13,Fthreatening widespread disruption to
OL,14,Fthe Bee bus and tram network.
OL,16,FThe union noted the impact will be
OL,17,Ffelt heavily on 19 December,
OL,18,Fhistorically a busy Friday for the
OL,19,Fcity's hospitality, and 20 December,
OL,20,Fwhich is usually the year's busiest
OL,21,Fshopping day.
