OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,FUnite regional industrial officer Sam
OL,7,FMarshall said: "The offer does nothing
OL,8,Fto increase basic pay, does not match
OL,9,Finflation, and fails to recognise the
OL,10,Fhigh level of responsibility and
OL,11,Fcommitment shown by these workers
OL,12,Fevery day.
OL,14,F"A resolution will only be possible if
OL,15,Fthe employer tables an offer that is
OL,16,Fmeaningfully better than the current
OL,17,Foffer."
