OL,3,CChaos expected as more transport staff
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,FSteve Warrener, Managing Director at
OL,7,FTfGM, said: "We continue to meet with
OL,8,Funion colleagues and hope we can
OL,9,Fresolve pay negotiations soon.
OL,11,F"The majority of TfGM's staff are
OL,12,Fstill working and are focused on
OL,13,Flimiting the impact on passengers on
OL,14,Fstrike days. Bus and trams services
OL,15,Fwill run as normal this weekend.
