OL,3,CChaos expected as more transport staff
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,F"We receive a mix of government and
OL,7,Flocal authority funding, as well as
OL,8,Fmoney from bus and tram fares. We have
OL,9,Fto therefore balance our commitments
OL,10,Fto good pay for our colleagues and low
OL,11,Ffares for passengers, with the
OL,12,Fchallenging financial climate in the
OL,13,Fpublic sector.
OL,15,F"We've explained to the unions that
OL,16,Fall the funding they refer to is
OL,17,Fgranted by government for us to invest
OL,18,Fin Greater Manchester's infrastructure
OL,19,Fand is ring-fenced to spend on capital
OL,20,Fprojects.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
