OL,3,CChaos expected as more transport staff
OL,4,Cstrike over pay
OL,6,F"We're absolutely committed to TfGM
OL,7,Fbeing a rewarding place to work and
OL,8,Fbuild a career, with good pay, terms
OL,9,Fand conditions.
OL,11,F"We've made several proposals to the
OL,12,Funions, accommodating their asks where
OL,13,Fwe can. Our current offer particularly
OL,14,Fsupports those on our lowest pay
OL,15,Fbands, ensuring that no-one earns less
OL,16,Fthan #15.10 per hour, the equivalent
OL,17,Fto an annual salary of over #29,000."
